---
Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 6
  Paragraph: 24
Title: The Great And Venerable Teacher
---
Master Ssu, Master Yu, Master Li, and Master Lai were all four talking
together. "Who can look upon nonbeing as his head, on life as his back,
and on death as his rump?" they said. "Who knows that life and death,
existence and annihilation, are all a single body? I will be his
friend!"
